rows.label: tlk41400021_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Puzzletree Wood is often used for
Gula's specialty woodcrafts!

rows.label: tlk41400021_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Its growth rings look like a puzzle, and
you can play with it as is, but most
importantly, it's easy to work with!

rows.label: tlk41400021_02_msg0003
rows.name:
From large things like houses to
small things like accessories!

rows.label: tlk41400021_02_msg0004
rows.name:
With Puzzletree Wood,
you can make anything.

rows.label: tlk41400021_02_msg0005
rows.name:
You can often gather Puzzletree Wood
from the trees around here, so
collecting some might come in handy!
